to the General's fried chicken.

57:07.624 --> 57:09.285
Smart Brother, how's it coming
with this antidote?

57:09.325 --> 57:12.624
I found one.
But it only works on
one person at a time.

57:12.662 --> 57:14.823
We have to stop
this thing at the source.

57:16.032 --> 57:17.795
Undercover Brother,
you're back!

57:17.834 --> 57:19.825
(alarm blaring)

57:23.907 --> 57:24.839
Hi.

57:24.874 --> 57:27.707
Hell's wrong with you bringing
a white girl in my house?

57:28.211 --> 57:29.473
