57:58.141 --> 58:00.166
"Roots"?
Maybe you've heard of it?

58:00.210 --> 58:04.203
It taught me such
a profound lesson about bigotry.

58:04.247 --> 58:07.114
I have sat on the sidelines
of race relations long enough.

58:07.150 --> 58:10.950
