58:20.663 --> 58:22.790
(chuckles)

58:22.832 --> 58:25.323
Son, you talk
a lot of shit.
Yes, I do.

58:25.368 --> 58:28.360
But you down.

58:28.671 --> 58:30.832
What?
Are you kidding?

58:30.874 --> 58:33.001
You're going to let the white boy
join just like that?

58:33.042 --> 58:35.237
I was in secret agent school
for three years!

58:35.278 --> 58:37.508
Three years.
I paid for them classes myself.

58:37.547 --> 58:40.175
- You made me.
- Smart Brother: Chief. Chief.

58:40.216 --> 58:42.081
I performed a full range
spectral analysis

58:42.118 --> 58:43.949
