brain waves.

58:43.987 --> 58:46.353
Then, I unlocked
her subconscious

58:46.389 --> 58:48.687
using a special form
of hypnosis.

58:48.725 --> 58:50.590
Then, I gently brushed
her hair.

58:50.627 --> 58:53.596
Then, I reached
deep within

58:53.630 --> 58:56.656
