and I found a list

58:56.699 --> 58:58.360
of The Man's targets.

58:58.401 --> 58:59.459
Good Lord.

58:59.502 --> 59:00.935
They're going after
James Brown

59:00.970 --> 59:02.801
tomorrow night
at the Grammys.

59:02.839 --> 59:05.569
We need to stop him.
Find the General and give him the antidote.

59:05.608 --> 59:08.076
That's right.
It's goin' to the streets. Hey, y'all!

59:08.111 --> 59:10.102
It's revolution
up in this bitch!

59:10.146 --> 59:12.444
Set the alarm
to def-con five!

59:12.482 --> 59:14.382
It's on, baby. It's on.

59:14.417 --> 59:16.578
- Good work, White She-Devil.
- Thanks.

59:16.619 --> 59:20.248
Oh, you in too.
What the fuck?! Chief!

59:20.290 --> 59:22.656
